      <title>经合组织在 G7 国家中上调英国经济增长预期，但警告通胀风险</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-25/oecd-upgrades-uk-growth-by-most-in-g-7-but-warns-on-inflation</link>
      <description><![CDATA[尽管人们对英国的潜在通胀压力仍存在担忧，但经合组织仍将英国未来两年的经济增速预期上调了，上调幅度超过其他七国集团成员国。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-25/oecd-upgrades-uk-growth-by-most-in-g-7-but-warns-on-inflation</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 25 Sep 2024 09:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>全球经济走出通胀危机 迈向稳定增长</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-25/global-economy-moves-beyond-inflation-crisis-to-stable-growth</link>
      <description><![CDATA[经合组织表示，随着强劲通胀压力缓解，全球经济正在步入新的稳定状态，各国央行得以继续谨慎放松政策。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-25/global-economy-moves-beyond-inflation-crisis-to-stable-growth</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 25 Sep 2024 09:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>汇丰银行改变欧洲央行利率决议，预计自 10 月起每次会议都将降息</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-25/hsbc-changes-ecb-call-sees-cut-every-meeting-starting-october</link>
      <description><![CDATA[汇丰银行经济学家表示，欧洲央行将在10月至4月期间的每次会议上开始降息。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-25/hsbc-changes-ecb-call-sees-cut-every-meeting-starting-october</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 25 Sep 2024 08:50:35 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>新世界集团考虑更换亿万富翁继承人郑志刚担任首席执行官</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-25/new-world-weighs-replacing-billionaire-heir-adrian-cheng-as-ceo</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，亿万富翁郑氏家族拥有的香港房地产开发商新世界发展有限公司正考虑更换第三代继承人郑志刚担任首席执行官，此前该公司因资产减记导致 20 年来首次出现年度亏损。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-25/new-world-weighs-replacing-billionaire-heir-adrian-cheng-as-ceo</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 25 Sep 2024 08:19:43 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>裕信银行的奥塞尔表示，他不会竞选德国商业银行董事会席位</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-25/unicredit-s-orcel-says-he-won-t-ask-for-commerzbank-board-seat</link>
      <description><![CDATA[意大利联合信贷银行 (UniCredit SpA) 首席执行官安德里亚·奥塞尔 (Andrea Orcel) 表示，他不会寻求德国商业银行 (Commerzbank AG) 的监事会席位，因为他正在评估该银行在日益激烈的反对声中追逐这家德国银行的下一步行动。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-25/unicredit-s-orcel-says-he-won-t-ask-for-commerzbank-board-seat</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 25 Sep 2024 07:34:52 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>韩国央行委员称房地产市场降温幅度未达预期前可能降息</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-25/bank-of-korea-may-cut-before-housing-cools-100-member-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一位董事会成员表示，韩国央行甚至可能在房地产市场出现明确降温迹象之前就下调基准利率，这表明支撑国内经济的需要日益增加。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-25/bank-of-korea-may-cut-before-housing-cools-100-member-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 25 Sep 2024 06:00:30 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>野村因操纵日本债券市场面临罚款</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-25/nomura-faces-fine-for-bond-market-manipulation-yomiuri-reports</link>
      <description><![CDATA[野村控股公司因涉嫌操纵日本政府债券期货市场而面临 2180 万日元（152,000 美元）的罚款，这对日本最大的经纪公司来说是一个在证券交易复苏期间的挫折。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-25/nomura-faces-fine-for-bond-market-manipulation-yomiuri-reports</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 25 Sep 2024 05:03:01 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中东冲突和中国刺激计划成为焦点，油价持续上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-24/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-sept-25</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于交易商关注中东局势发展和中国刺激措施对需求的影响，油价保持了一周多以来的最大涨幅。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-24/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-sept-25</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 24 Sep 2024 23:36:25 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>标普 500 指数创纪录后美国期货下跌；SAP 暴跌：市场综述</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-24/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[标普 500 指数今年第 41 次创下收盘纪录，美国股指期货小幅走低。美国国债和美元趋于稳定。]]></description>
